TI  - OpenSAFELY: factors associated with COVID-19-related hospital death in the linked electronic health records of 17 million adult NHS patients.
AU  - Collaborative, The OpenSAFELY
AU  - Williamson, Elizabeth
AU  - Walker, Alex J.
AU  - Bhaskaran, Krishnan J.
AU  - Bacon, Seb
