TI  - Revealing the microscale spatial signature of dengue transmission and immunity in an urban population
AU  - Salje, Henrik
AU  - Lessler, Justin
AU  - Endy, Timothy P.
AU  - Curriero, Frank C.
AU  - Gibbons, Robert V.
AU  - Nisalak, Ananda
