TI  - Country-report pattern corrections of new cases allow accurate two-week predictions of Covid19 evolution with the Gompertz mode
AU  - Villanueva, I.
AU  - Conesa, D.
AU  - Català, M.
AU  - Cano, López
AU  - Perramon, A.
AU  - Molinuevo, D.
