TI  - Real-time decision-making during emergency disease outbreaks
AU  - Probert, William J. M.
AU  - Jewell, Chris P.
AU  - Werkman, Marleen
AU  - Fonnesbeck, Christopher J.
AU  - Goto, Yoshitaka
