TI  - Adding ‘iterativity’ to the credibility, relevance, legitimacy: A novel scheme to highlight dynamic aspects of science–policy interfaces
AU  - Sarkki, Simo
AU  - Tinch, Rob
AU  - Niemelä, Jari
