TI  - Modelling practices, data provisioning, sharing and dissemination needs for pandemic decision-making: a European survey-based modellers’ perspective, 2020 to 2022
AU  - van Kleef, Esther
AU  - Van Bortel, Wim
AU  - Arsevska, Elena
AU  - Busani, Luca
AU  - Dellicour, Simon
AU  - Di Domenico, Laura
AU  - Gilbert, Marius
