TI  - Getting the most out of maths: How to coordinate mathematical modelling research to support a pandemic, lessons learnt from three initiatives that were part of the COVID-19 response in the UK
AU  - Dangerfield, Ciara E.
AU  - David Abrahams, I.
AU  - Budd, Chris
AU  - Butchers, Matt
AU  - Cates, Michael E.
AU  - Champneys, Alan R.
AU  - Currie, Christine S. M.
